node.text: About 8, 9 months ago Sam sends me this song called To Die For. He tells me he wants to make a video where he’s a mannequin and through the glass he watches couples and people passing by, time passes, and so forth. I listen to the song and it disarms me. I wasn’t expecting it to effect me the way it did. @samsmith thank you for trusting me with this song - i know how much it means to you, for waiting for me so I could do this, and for being a true gem of a person and the greatest collaborator and friend a guy could ask for.
